Protocol: MultiEncrypt AnB

Types:
    Agent A,B;
    Number Msg,Nonce1,Nonce2,empty;
    Function [Agent -> PublicKey] pk,sk

Knowledge:
    A: A,B,pk,sk,inv(pk(A)),inv(sk(A)),empty;
    B: A,B,pk,sk,inv(pk(B)),inv(sk(B)),empty

Actions:
    A -> B: {Nonce1,B}pk(B)
    B -> A: {Nonce1,A}pk(A)
    A -> B: {Nonce2,B}pk(B)
    B -> A: {Nonce2,A}pk(A)
    
Goals:

   Nonce1 secret between A,B
   Nonce2 secret between A,B
